{"id":874,"date":"2024-08-02T21:02:03","date_gmt":"2024-08-02T21:02:03","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=874"},"modified":"2024-08-02T21:02:03","modified_gmt":"2024-08-02T21:02:03","slug":"tm072-avalanche","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/tm072-avalanche\/","title":{"rendered":"TM072 Avalanche"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">TM072 Avalanche<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td>Frost Mountain 2F<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Description<\/th>\n<td>An attack move that gains in intensity if the target has hurt the user.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>PP<\/th>\n<td>10<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Type<\/th>\n<td>Ice<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Prerequisites<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Have access to Frost Mountain<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Enter Frost Mountain and start by going North.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/01-pokemon-unbound-going-north-after-entering-frost-mountain.jpg\" alt=\"Going North after entering Frost Mountain. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Going North after entering Frost Mountain.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Take the first turn West and walk past the NPC with glasses.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/02-pokemon-unbound-taking-the-1st-turn-west.jpg\" alt=\"Taking the first turn West. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Taking the first turn West.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Continue going West and jump over the ledge before going South.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/03-pokemon-unbound-jumping-down-from-the-ledge-and-going-south.jpg\" alt=\"Jumping down from the ledge and going South. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Jumping down from the ledge and going South.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll see stairs to your East taking you to a higher platform. Take the ladder on the platform to go to the second floor.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/04-pokemon-unbound-climbing-the-ladder-on-the-rocky-platform.jpg\" alt=\"Climbing the ladder on the rocky platform. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Climbing the ladder on the rocky platform.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Now, climb the stairs ahead of you and continue following the narrow path West.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/05-pokemon-unbound-going-west-after-reaching-the-2nd-floor.jpg\" alt=\"Going West after reaching the second floor. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Going West after reaching the second floor.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The TM for Avalanche is at the end of the path.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/06-pokemon-unbound-finding-the-tm-for-avalanche-at-the-end-of-the-path.jpg\" alt=\"Finding the TM for Avalanche at the end of the path. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Finding the TM for Avalanche at the end of the path.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc.png 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/p